title: GateioExchange
author: GateioExchange
content: Is Web 3 becoming more popular than Web 2 for developers?   The Eth.JS library became THE MOST downloaded javascript library, surpassing stripe credit card payments for devs.  Also we discuss one of the Ethereum developers going out on his own to make his own blockchain.  All this and more on Gate.io News:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RtI-9k-y3BU
